{{Quote|He's as good at destroying Wookiee culture as dropping corpses full of Ardroxian Flu.|Jolee Bindo, on the subject of [[Chuundar]]|<ref name="KOTOR" />}}
The '''Ardroxian Flu''' was a type of disease. It was known to be carried within the remains of corpses, and was possibly capable of infecting numerous non-[[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Species/Legends|species]] including, apparently, [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]]. It was mentioned by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jolee Bindo]] as an analogy for how he perceived the impact that [[Chuundar]], the onetime [[Chief/Legends|Chieftain]] of [[Rwookrrorro/Legends|Rwookrrorro Village]], and his dealings with [[Czerka Arms/Legends|Czerka Corporation]] had on the culture of the Wookiee homeworld of [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]].

